  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p720190/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img height=\"293\" src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201502/9f43fc4e2e1e4b918ca346906fe278e0.jpg\" width=\"440\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tNetflix <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/scramble\" target=\"_blank\">scrambled</a> on Wednesday after accidentally posting 10 episodes of the political drama's third season - two weeks ahead of its scheduled release date of Friday, Feb. 27.Netflix周三意外发布即将开播的《纸牌屋》第三季前十集掀起了轩然大波&mdash;&mdash;《纸牌屋》第三季的开播时间应该是27日，也就是说提早两周就被提前曝光。</p>\n<p>\n\tMere minutes after the leak was reported - but not before I was able to load the first episode and eventually watch it in its entirety - Netflix solved the problem, and viewers who attempted to get a jump on binge-watching Season 3 were met with a screen that read, &quot;Watch Season 3 on February 27.&quot; The official House of Cards Twitter maintained a sense of humor about the incident, posting the following message:在视频泄露一段时间后&mdash;&mdash;但是还没来得及让人完整下载或者是观看第一集的时候&mdash;&mdash;Netflix就迅速把视频下架了。想再次进入的观众看到的指示&ldquo;敬请期待第三季2月27日回归&rdquo;。《纸牌屋》在Twitter上的官方微博也针对这一事件发推：</p>\n<p>\n\tThis is Washington. There's always a leak. All 13 episodes will launch February 27.这里是华盛顿。视频泄漏还是发生了。2月27日将会发布全部13集。</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p720190/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p720190\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p628712/\">情人节 达令的多种英文表达你造吗</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 